    <pre>Kahn Academy, a learning site, has this feature. Look at <a href="http://www.khanacademy.org/exercisedashboard">http://www.khanacademy.org/exercisedashboard</a> where you can do exercises. You can start doing tests, and it will be saved in your session. A bar at the top of the screen shows you your progress and achievements and tells you to log in to save the progress. This is a great way to get people to create an account, as they don't want to loose their progress.

